center61982 and 1986 TOP GOALSCORERS Section::::Top goalscorers .
With 11 goals in five matches in 1954 , Sándor Kocsis beat Brazilian Ademir 's existing record of nine goals in one tournament from 1950 .
However , only four years later the record was in turn beaten by Just Fontaine . !
